{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "Automation"}], "prev": {"link": "../create_a_workflow/", "title": "Workflows: Creating a Workflow via an Automation Tab"}, "next": {"link": "../dial_by_extension_block/", "title": "Workflows: Adding a Dial by Extension Block"}, "title": "Workflows: Designing a Workflow", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"workflows-designing-a-workflow\">\n<h1>Workflows: Designing a Workflow<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#workflows-designing-a-workflow\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\">There are a lot of customizations available to create a unique workflow within the Maha Platform for the contacts enrolled in the workflow.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">Designing a workflow using the following steps allows you to edit an existing workflow.</div>\n<div class=\"line\">Refer to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/new_workflow.html\">Creating a New Workflow</a> to create a new workflow.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Automation</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Workflows</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click on a workflow</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Design Workflow</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>You can add a new block to your workflow by clicking and dragging the desired block to the workflow</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p><strong>Email</strong>: <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_text_block.html\">Text</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_divider_block.html\">Divider</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_image_block.html\">Image</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_button_block.html\">Button</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_preference_block.html\">Preferences</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_social_share_block.html\">Social Share</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_social_follow_block.html\">Social Follow</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_video_block.html\">Video</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/emails/email_web_version_block.html\">Web Version</a></p></li>\n<li><p><strong>SMS</strong>: <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_message_block.html\">Send Message</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/ask_question_block.html\">Ask Question</a></p></li>\n<li><p><strong>Voice</strong>: <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/play_recording_block.html\">Play Recording</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/speak_text_block.html\">Speak Text</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/go_to_menu_block.html\">Goto Menu</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_by_extension_block.html\">Dial by Extension</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_by_name_block.html\">Dial by Name</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_menu_block.html\">Dial Menu</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/forward_call_block.html\">Forward Call</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/voicemail_block.html\">Voicemail</a></p></li>\n<li><p><strong>SMS and Voice</strong>: <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/if_then_block.html\">If/Then</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/wait_block.html\">Wait</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_goal_block.html\">Set Goal</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/set_variable_block.html\">Set Variable</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/time_of_day_block.html\">Time of Day</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_property_block.html\">Update Property</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_consent_block.html\">Update Consent</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_lists_block.html\">Update Lists</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/update_topics_block.html\">Update Topics</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/enroll_in_a_workflow_block.html\">Enroll in Workflow</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_email_block.html\">Send Email</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_sms_block.html\">Send SMS</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_email_block.html\">Send Internal Email</a>, <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/send_internal_sms_block.html\">Send Internal SMS</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>This will trigger a new tab where you can customize the block</p></li>\n<li><p>To edit an already created block, hover over the block and click <i class=\"fa fa-pencil\"></i> and make changes in the tab</p></li>\n<li><p>To duplicate a block, hover over the block and click <i class=\"fa fa-files-o\"></i></p></li>\n<li><p>To delete a block, hover over the block and click <i class=\"fa fa-trash-o\"></i></p></li>\n<li><p>To rearrange the blocks, drag the created blocks around the template</p></li>\n<li><p>When you are satisfied with your workflow, click <strong>Publish Version</strong>.</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>To view your version history, click <strong>Versions</strong> and click on desired version</p></li>\n<li><p>To restore a previous version of your workflow, click <strong>Revert to Version</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>You can also publish a workflow from this page, by clicking <strong>Publish Version</strong></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/automation/guides/workflows/dial_by_extension_block", "Workflows: Adding a Dial by Extension Block", "N", "next"], ["users/automation/guides/workflows/create_a_workflow", "Workflows: Creating a Workflow via an Automation Tab", "P", "previous"]], "sourcename": "users/automation/guides/workflows/design_a_workflow.rst.txt", "toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Workflows: Designing a Workflow</a></li>\n</ul>\n", "display_toc": false, "page_source_suffix": ".rst", "current_page_name": "users/automation/guides/workflows/design_a_workflow", "sidebars": ["localtoc.html", "relations.html", "sourcelink.html", "searchbox.html"], "customsidebar": null, "favicon_url": null, "logo_url": null, "alabaster_version": "0.7.12"}